==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Namesake
<hw>Name"sake`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[For <ets>name's
sake</ets>; <it>i. e.</it>, one named for the sake of another's
name.]</ety> <def>One that has the same name as another; especially, one
called after, or named out of regard to, another.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nammu</ent>⟦br⟧
